                            <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/11589: Telegram</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The Commander in Chief, United States Asiatic
                                    Fleet</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Yarnell</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the Chief of
                                    Naval Operations</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Leahy</hi></persName>)<note n="19" xml:id="d892fn19">Copy
                                    transmitted to the Department by the Navy
                                Department.</note></head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Shanghai</hi></placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1937-12-13T21:40:00+08:00">December 13, 1937—9:40
                                        p.m.</date><lb/>[Received December 13—9:10 a.m.]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>0013. General Matsui’s headquarters announced capture Nanking,
                                Chinese troops surrendering unconditionally.</p>
